### SimpleMDB API Test - REST Client
### Use the REST Client extension in VS Code to run these requests

### ========== MOVIES ENDPOINTS ==========

### List Movies (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies?page=1&size=5

### List Movies (Error - Invalid page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies?page=0&size=5

### Create Movie (Success)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "year": 2010,
  "description": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through dream-sharing technology."
}

### Create Movie (Error - Missing title)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "year": 2010,
  "description": "Test"
}

### Read Movie (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/1

### Read Movie (Error - Not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/999

### Update Movie (Success)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Shawshank Redemption - Updated",
  "year": 1994,
  "description": "Updated description."
}

### Update Movie (Error - Invalid year)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test",
  "year": 1500,
  "description": "Test"
}

### Delete Movie (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/3

### Delete Movie (Error - Not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/999

### Get Actors by Movie (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/1/actors?page=1&size=5

### Get Actors by Movie (Error - Invalid page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/movies/1/actors?page=0&size=5

### ========== ACTORS ENDPOINTS ==========

### List Actors (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors?page=1&size=5

### List Actors (Error - Invalid size)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors?page=1&size=0

### Create Actor (Success)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Leonardo DiCaprio",
  "birthYear": 1974,
  "nationality": "American"
}

### Create Actor (Error - Missing name)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "birthYear": 1974,
  "nationality": "American"
}

### Read Actor (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/1

### Read Actor (Error - Not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/999

### Update Actor (Success)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morgan Freeman - Updated",
  "birthYear": 1937,
  "nationality": "American"
}

### Update Actor (Error - Invalid birth year)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "birthYear": 1500,
  "nationality": "Test"
}

### Delete Actor (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/3

### Delete Actor (Error - Not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/999

### Get Movies by Actor (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/1/movies?page=1&size=5

### Get Movies by Actor (Error - Invalid page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors/1/movies?page=-1&size=5

### ========== USERS ENDPOINTS ==========

### List Users (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users?page=1&size=5

### List Users (Error - Invalid page)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users?page=0&size=5

### Create User (Success)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@smdb.com",
  "role": "User"
}

### Create User (Error - Invalid email)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "invalidemail",
  "role": "User"
}

### Read User (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1

### Read User (Error - Not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/999

### Update User (Success)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin-updated",
  "email": "admin@smdb.com",
  "role": "Admin"
}

### Update User (Error - Missing username)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "role": "User"
}

### Delete User (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/2

### Delete User (Error - Not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/999

### ========== ACTORS-MOVIES ENDPOINTS ==========

### List Actors-Movies (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies?page=1&size=5

### List Actors-Movies (Error - Invalid size)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies?page=1&size=-1

### Create Actor-Movie (Success)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actorId": 1,
  "movieId": 2,
  "role": "Supporting Actor"
}

### Create Actor-Movie (Error - Invalid actorId)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actorId": 0,
  "movieId": 1,
  "role": "Test Role"
}

### Read Actor-Movie (Success)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/1

### Read Actor-Movie (Error - Not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/999

### Update Actor-Movie (Success)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actorId": 1,
  "movieId": 1,
  "role": "Updated Role"
}

### Update Actor-Movie (Error - Missing role)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actorId": 1,
  "movieId": 1,
  "role": ""
}

### Delete Actor-Movie (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/3

### Delete Actor-Movie (Error - Not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/actors-movies/999
